  <TD>
     <!WA40><A HREF="http://www.cs.wustl.edu/cs/playground/papers.html"><STRONG> Publications </STRONG></A><P>
     These <!WA41><A HREF="http://www.cs.wustl.edu/cs/playground/papers.html">papers</A> describe the programming model and
     software tools in more detail.
  </TD>
